data.description: Welcome to Meadow Run in the original Menifee neighborhood of Menifee Lakes. This lovely home features a formal living and dining room at entry. (Dont forget to check out the not so hidden room under the stairs) The family room has a fireplace and is adjacent to the lovely kitchen with stainless steel appliances that overlooks the back yard. Upstairs are the bedrooms, all great in size, and the primary has a fireplace and an ensuite featuring large shower with soaking tub and ample closet space. This home has recent upgrades to flooring and comes with SMART light switches, thermostat, fire detectors and financed solar to help keep energy costs down. The backyard is a great place to relax, with covered patio and room for kids and pets to play. Wheatfield Park, Bell Mountain Middle School and Mt San Jacinto College are just a quick jaunt away. The park has an impressive 4th of July fireworks display and the city routinely has events at the college. Menifee Lakes is a 35 acre man made lake that is private to the residents and is perfect for an evening stroll or catching some fish. Meadow Run is priced to sell. Make the SMART choice and come see this home today!
